ave time<\/strong> \u2013 Activating Merlin with shortcuts (<strong>Ctrl + M<\/strong> or <strong>Cmd + M<\/strong>) lets you use it across webpages instantly, making your workflow faster.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Explore the prompt library<\/strong> \u2013 Save common prompts you use frequently. This helps you access them quickly and maintain a consistent tone in generated responses.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Experiment with multiple models<\/strong> \u2013 Each AI model offers unique strengths. Try GPT-4 for detailed answers or Claude for concise summaries to find what works best for each task.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Alternatives to Merlin AI<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/chatgpt.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ChatGPT (OpenAI)<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 ChatGPT offers conversational AI powered by OpenAI\u2019s GPT models. It\u2019s ideal for generating detailed responses, drafting, and brainstorming but is more limited in integrations compared to Merlin AI.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.perplexity.ai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Perplexity AI<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Perplexity AI is a web-based tool that excels at answering questions and summarizing information from the web. With real-time internet access, it\u2019s a good choice for quick fact-checking and research summaries.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.jasper.ai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jasper AI<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Jasper is a content creation AI tool popular among marketers. It provides templates for various content types, like blogs and ads, with a focus on customization, but it lacks Merlin\u2019s extensive integrations.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/writesonic.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writesonic<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Writesonic is geared toward creating high-quality written content for businesses. It specializes in long-form content,